info.abstract:
[Type]
Management.

[Behaviour]
Start, stop and get information about workers.

[Parameters]
- action : use one of the following types:
	"info": get information about workers deployed by the user (default);
	"info_workers": get information about all the workers (reserved to administrators);
	"deploy": try to starts workers;
	"undeploy": stop workers.
- number : number of workers to be started.
- user_filter : filter on username in case action "info_workers" is selected (reserved to administrators).

[System parameters]
- exec_mode : operator execution mode. Possible values are async (default) for
              asynchronous mode, sync for synchronous mode with json-compliant output.
- objkey_filter : filter on the output of the operator written to file (default=all => no filter, none => no output):
                  workers_summary : show workers status;
                  workers_list : show workers list;
                  workers_list_summary : show workers list summary;
                  workers_user : show workers user list (reserved to administrators);
                  workers_user_summary : show workers user list summary (reserved to administrators).
- save : set to "yes" (default) in case output has to be saved remotely.

[Examples]       
Start 3 workers:
OPH_TERM: oph_pav_worker action=deploy;number=3;
SUBMISSION STRING: "operator=oph_pav_worker;action=deploy;number=3;"
